Hi,
Greetings from Envisage team (Tech-Ambience).

Applicaions are open for Tech-Ambience coordinators.
From this year, Envisage is also handling *Tech-Ambience projects of
Shaastra*. The role of a tech-ambience coordinator is to create ambience
projects for Shaastra 2017 using cutting edge technology. These projects
will be put up at various locations throughout Shaastra whose primary aim
will be to give audience the feel of technology by letting them interact.
Few projects proposed are footstep piano
<https://youtu.be/OrmWMejvmFU>, interactive
wall <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xFgvNMN2DiQ>, quadrepedal bot
<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kKSDgIhc8GI>, rain room
<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7cem71cR0S0>,

Interested students can fill up this form
<https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSddqjN4aCnFTW3SVK1Q1SOir5aIozUcnzM7dAg_yqiajq6uIw/viewform>
.

*Eligibilty: Current 2nd years and above undergraduates*.
*Deadline: 11:50 pm, 28th September 2017*

